      "created_at": "2022-01-23T18:13:56.243Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi Alex!</p>\n<p>So, I have my ride in July and my plan from Coach Jack. So, how often should I test using say the TD Ramp Test? Does Coach Jack schedule them into the plan? Should the test just be added into the plan as an extra workout or should they be substituted for  certain rides in the plan at certain points in the plan? Thanks for yours and others thoughts!</p>",
